{"tid":1432599,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"團體警總外聲援警方 支持嚴正執法","createTime":"2019-08-08T09:22:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T09:27:54.000Z","uid":188430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f33aaaab3d370bad00cd23435c1e062af7ae40fc","tid":1432599,"uid":188430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:22:28.000Z","msg":"曾經舉辦撐警集會的團體「香港政研會」，今日（8日）中午有約50人在灣仔警察總部外集會，高叫「踢走暴徒」、「支持嚴正執法」等口號，聲援警方。<br />\n     香港政研會主席鄧德成表示，收集市民意見後，政研會總結了11項訴求，包括重啟《逃犯條例》修訂，指紛亂的根源來自修例，假如重啟修例並得以通過，市民才會明白修例並不影響日常生活，鄧德成強調並非與政府現時政策唱反調。<br />\n     政研會其餘的訴求還包括成立獨立調查委員會，調查反對派立法會議員有否協助或煽動暴動，至於調查警方濫權則應該交由監警會負責。政研會又要求馬上展開廿三條立法、訂立辱警罪等。"},{"pid":"603896a19a514f3dfdcb86ad69aa336301b3b6bc","tid":1432599,"uid":76922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1df06gr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1df06gr.png&h=8c2fa3c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u0QkmPM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu0QkmPM.png&h=716e9254&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yvQDSWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyvQDSWs.png&h=d18ba813&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0kE9e9N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0kE9e9N.jpg&h=65fe498a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7f2ZCn8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7f2ZCn8.jpg&h=e0b4dc49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FOZdGPO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFOZdGPO.jpg&h=bef09638&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0cbaea423c6abea6434312fe7f38c51f9f73c50","tid":1432599,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:27:54.000Z","msg":"黑警記者會終於講返句人話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1432578\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https:/